  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "auKyvy18kXJ4wI7A6FYlPcOBYTk=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "The Operational Hub provides crypto-native financial infrastructure as add-on services:\n\n**Setup services:**\n- Exchange account setup (Kraken, Coinbase, Binance, Bitfinex, Crypto.com, Nexo)\n- Crypto-friendly bank setup\n- Payment provider & off-ramp setup for fiat conversion\n- EOR/PEO setup for local payroll providers\n\n**Ongoing compliance:**\n- Payment controls & reconciliation \u2014 crypto payments requiring second-party approval based on invoices\n- AML monitoring & compliance reporting \u2014 regular checks on contractors/clients for sanctions, PEP status; wallet risk assessment\n- Supplier & partner liaison \u2014 maintaining accounts with EORs/PEOs to reduce offboarding risk\n- Invoice compliance review \u2014 ensuring invoices meet local law requirements before payment\n- Card & spend operations \u2014 monitoring connected accounts, creating cards/users, flagging restricted transactions\n- Contractor documentation support \u2014 income/affiliation docs for visas, loans\n- Legal counsel advice \u2014 5 hours of Swiss counsel included\n\nMulti-currency payouts support USD, GBP, EUR, CHF, and DKK with 48-hour transfers. Additional currencies available on request.",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z"
    }
  },
